but he also said he expects a tougher time ahead when he begins 
grappling with more contentious issues such as the budget he 
stepped away from the most controversial item of his first week in 
office a suggestion to place a premium on savings accounts to help 
rescue the savings and loan industry he said the proposal hadnt 
yet reached his desk 
