913 per share on revenue of 15 billion up 11 percent from 
1987s earnings of 313 million or 775 per share revenue in 1987 
was 137 billion 
earnings for the year increased in all segments except 
information systems the company said combat aircraft and space 
systems and missiles recorded the largest gains 
